profile:
Lawns & Beds | Hedges & Trees | Weeds & Pests 

Top quality service at a reasonable price. CTM Lawn Care can provide all your lawn maintenance and landscape needs. 

Call or visit our website for a free estimate. 

LAWN CARE Mow, Trim, and Blow Edging & Walks Fertilise & Lime Weed & Pest Control Dethatch & Aerate Over seed and Top Dress 

BEDS & HEDGES Mulch Edging Trim and Prune 

INSTALL & RENOVATE Lawns & Beds Leaf clean up Seed & Sod Tree Removal 

Registered, licensed, certified, and insured. Payment options cash, cheque, etransfer, paypal, visa, or mastercard. Monthly invoices, with weekly, monthly, and annual payment plans. 

CTM Lawn Care | 902-957-3571
